      "time": 6.37,
      "time_str": "00:06.370",
      "text": "光光:我想着你的美丽和温柔",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 9.25,
      "time_str": "00:09.250",
      "text": "我想牵你的手",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 11.5,
      "time_str": "00:11.500",
      "text": "也许没有你的日子我会怎样度过",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 14.47,
      "time_str": "00:14.470",
      "text": "也不知道该怎样子度过",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 17.32,
      "time_str": "00:17.320",
      "text": "我的眼泪不停流",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 20.15,
      "time_str": "00:20.150",
      "text": "我的心被你看透",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 23.02,
      "time_str": "00:23.020",
      "text": "此刻你是否懂得我多难受",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 29.02,
      "time_str": "00:29.020",
      "text": "K-Bo:我是如此的想你",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 31.87,
      "time_str": "00:31.870",
      "text": "每晚我都自己问自己",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 37.73,
      "time_str": "00:37.730",
      "text": "决心忘记可是又不断的想起",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 43.52,
      "time_str": "00:43.520",
      "text": "最后才明白 你是我的唯一",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 50.36,
      "time_str": "00:50.360",
      "text": "光光:我看见 你在我眼前出现",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 55.95,
      "time_str": "00:55.950",
      "text": "K-Bo:我听见 说爱却不是永远",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
